# Large generated artifacts kept on local disk only (exceed GitHub limits / regenerable).
# Raw population source of truth — regenerable via research/profile_generation scripts:
research/profile_generation/results/
# Intermediate trips monolith — regenerated by export_to_viz.py before chunking into andorra_trips_{0..5}.json:
app/public/model/andorra_trips.json
# Vite production build output for the main app — regenerated by `npm run build` / Vercel:
app/dist/

